4 anyāyāṃ śaktau naivāvasthānam karoti;
5 ayam ca saḥ pakṣaḥ pratipakṣaḥ asti tasya mithyādarśanasya,
6 yaḥ manyate asmābhiḥ uttamātmā anyasyātmāno 'dhi jāyate.

7 Ata eva, yadā śruyate vā dṛśyate
8 yat ātmānaṃ balavattākaraṣati,
9 gacchati kālaḥ na ca naraḥ paśyati;

13 Asya aham satyām anubhūtim alabham,
14 tam ātmānam śṛṇvan viśmayan ca kurvan;
15 hi pañcāśat paryāyāḥ ārūḍhāḥ āsīt

25 Sanleo-sthale vasasi Noli-sthale ca ava-gacchasi,
26 Bismantova-parvate Cacume-parvate ca āruhya gacchasi
27 caraṇābhyām; atra tu āvaśyakam puruṣasya utpaptum;

37 Sa ca mama: "Na tava padaṃ patatu;
38 kim tarhi mama paścād aśailam āruhya,
39 yāvat kasmāt prajñātāraḥ ko 'pi dṛśyeta."

55 Adau dṛṣṭim anīyayām nīca-tīreṣu;
56 tataḥ sūryāya utthāpayām āsa, paśyāmi ca
57 vāma-diśataḥ āhataḥ asmākam.

94 tadā tvam asya mārgasya ante bhaviṣyasi;
95 tatra tava śrama-nivṛttir abhīkṣitā.
96 Adhikaṃ na bruve, idam ca jānāmi satyam iti."

121 Tasya pravṛttayaḥ mandāḥ vacasaśca hrasvāḥ
122 Mama oṣṭhau hasitam artham anīyatām alikam;
123 Tataḥ aham ārabdhaḥ: "He Belācca, mama na duḥkham

133 yadi prārthanā prathamam na māṃ sahayate
134 yā hṛdayāt anugraheṇa jīvanāt svargam ārohati;
135 anyā kim prayojanam, yā svarge na śrūyate?».
